snippet.title: Global Farmer | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
GLOBAL FARMER | OUT NOW

Based on real-world data from OpenStreetMap, you can manage your farm anywhere in the world. Explore your own neighborhood from the perspective of a budding farmer, or try to become a successful agriculture magnate in all
other locations on the planet.

Check it out here: https://links.aerosoft.com/GlobalFarmer
